info.name: OAuth 2.0 Authorization Server Detection Template
author: righettod
info.description: Try to detect OAuth 2.0 Authorization Server via the "oauth/token" endpoint

request:
POST /oauth/token HTTP/1.1
Host: pastek.fabrique.social.gouv.fr
User-Agent: Nuclei - Open-source project (github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei)
Connection: close
Content-Length: 117
Accept: */*
Accept-Language: en
Accept-Encoding: gzip

grant_type=authorization_code&client_id=xxx&redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fprojectdiscovery.io&code=xxx&client_secret=xxx
response:
HTTP/1.1 401 Unauthorized
Connection: close
Transfer-Encoding: chunked
Cache-Control: private, no-store
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Date: Sat, 09 Oct 2021 16:04:27 GMT
Pragma: no-cache
Server: nginx
Www-Authenticate: Bearer realm="Doorkeeper", error="invalid_client", error_description="Client authentication failed due to unknown client, no client authentication included, or unsupported authentication method."
X-Request-Id: dfde657d-7632-479e-893d-c3125695fa6a
X-Runtime: 0.018945

{"error":"invalid_client","error_description":"Client authentication failed due to unknown client, no client authentication included, or unsupported authentication method."}
